msgid "Step by step"
msgstr "Крок за кроком"

#: ../../dispatcher/finite_state_machine/index.rst:38
msgid ""
"Before handle any states you will need to specify what kind of states you"
" want to handle"
msgstr ""
"Перед обробкою будь-которых станив Вам потрибно буде указать тип станив, которые"
" Ви хотите обробляти"

#: ../../dispatcher/finite_state_machine/index.rst:43
msgid "And then write handler for each state separately from the start of dialog"
msgstr ""
"А потим напишить обробник (handler) для каждого стану окремо от початку "
"диалогу"

#: ../../dispatcher/finite_state_machine/index.rst:45
msgid ""
"Here is dialog can be started only via command :code:`/start`, so lets "
"handle it and make transition user to state :code:`Form.name`"
msgstr ""
